{"id":305,"date":"2019-08-04T15:31:11","date_gmt":"2019-08-04T08:31:11","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/?p=305"},"modified":"2019-08-04T15:31:11","modified_gmt":"2019-08-04T08:31:11","slug":"thiet-ke-noi-that-gia-dinh-can-ghi-nho-dieu-nay-cho-gia-chu-menh-moc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"http:\/\/kientruc2.ninhbinhweb.info\/thiet-ke-noi-that-gia-dinh-can-ghi-nho-dieu-nay-cho-gia-chu-menh-moc\/","title":{"rendered":"Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t gia \u0111\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ghi nh\u1edb \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho gia ch\u1ee7 m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><strong>Trong 5 b\u1ea3n m\u1ec7nh thu\u1ed9c thuy\u1ebft Ng\u0169 h\u00e0nh, M\u1ed9c l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng cho s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb r\u1ec5, th\u00e2n, nh\u00e1nh v\u00e0 l\u00e1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng ty N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng t\u00f4n vinh s\u1eafc xanh cho n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch<\/h2>\n<p>Thuy\u1ebft Ng\u0169 h\u00e0nh, h\u01b0\u1edbng phong th\u1ee7y c\u1ee7a m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c l\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng v\u00e0 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u00ean m\u1edf c\u1eeda ch\u00ednh theo nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<p>M\u1ed1i t\u01b0\u01a1ng sinh: M\u1ed9c sinh H\u1ecfa v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Th\u1ee7y t\u01b0\u01a1ng sinh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean l\u00fd cho vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cho gia ch\u1ee7 m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u00f4ng m\u00e0u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c l\u00e0 m\u00e0u xanh, ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u00e0u \u0111en, xanh d\u01b0\u01a1ng. Trong l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn\u00a0<strong>n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch<\/strong>, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 sofa m\u00e0u xanh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u1ed1m nh\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn xanh l\u00e1 \u0111\u1eadm. Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian m\u00e1t m\u1ebb, g\u1ea7n g\u0169i.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_65222\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-65222 size-full lazyloaded lazy-load-active\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638.jpg 690w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638-250x185.jpg 250w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638-406x300.jpg 406w\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"510\" data-src=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638.jpg 690w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638-250x185.jpg 250w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638-406x300.jpg 406w\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-65222\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638.jpg 690w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638-250x185.jpg 250w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638-406x300.jpg 406w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" data-lazy-src=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26233576_1590278797705986_8295600433299340414_o-e1515634118638.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-65222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">B\u1ea1n n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn\u00a0b\u1ed9 sofa\u00a0m\u00e0u xanh c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1eafc \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eeb c\u1ed1m nh\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ebfn xanh \u0111\u1eadm.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>M\u00e0u n\u00e2u c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c. S\u1eafc n\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn showroom c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng ty N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ecdn nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9 sofa g\u1ed7 \u00f3c ch\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0u caf\u00e9 \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch. Chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf sofa th\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i showroom c\u1ee7a N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 sofa g\u1ed7 \u00f3c ch\u00f3 m\u00e0u n\u00e2u cafe, k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u00e0n tr\u00e0 c\u00f9ng tone v\u00e0 k\u1ec7 tivi thanh tho\u00e1t \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c to\u00e1t l\u00ean v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p gi\u1ea3n d\u1ecb m\u00e0 sang tr\u1ecdng. Ho\u1eb7c, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn sofa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ecdc da m\u00e0u n\u00e2u, thu\u1eadn theo m\u00e0u t\u01b0\u01a1ng sinh c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c.<\/p>\n<div id=\"attachment_65220\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-65220 size-full lazyloaded lazy-load-active\" src=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297.jpg\" sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" srcset=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297.jpg 690w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297-250x161.jpg 250w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297-465x300.jpg 465w\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"445\" data-src=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297.jpg 690w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297-250x161.jpg 250w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297-465x300.jpg 465w\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-65220\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297.jpg 690w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297-250x161.jpg 250w, https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297-465x300.jpg 465w\" data-lazy-sizes=\"(max-width: 690px) 100vw, 690px\" data-lazy-src=\"https:\/\/noithatducduong.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/26221244_1590278707705995_7329409425268191400_o-e1515634136297.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" \/><\/p>\n<p id=\"caption-attachment-65220\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">R\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e0i l\u1ed9c b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ed9\u00a0sofa g\u1ed7 \u00f3c ch\u00f3<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>N\u1ebfu ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed9ng, \u0111\u1eebng ti\u1ebfc ti\u1ec1n s\u1eafm th\u00eam k\u1ec7 trang tr\u00ed, t\u1ee7 r\u01b0\u1ee3u. N\u1ebfu b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 tr\u01b0ng b\u00e0y r\u01b0\u1ee3u, \u1eaft h\u1eb3n kh\u00e1ch tin r\u1eb1ng: Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1edfng r\u01b0\u1ee3u v\u00e0 c\u1ef1c k\u00ec hi\u1ebfu kh\u00e1ch. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 khi, ch\u00e9n r\u01b0\u1ee3u l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n!<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi tung ra nh\u1eefng thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf k\u1ec7 trang tr\u00ed nhi\u1ec1u ng\u0103n. N\u00e9t tinh t\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng hoa u\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1ee3n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho nh\u1eefng v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean t\u1eebng ng\u0103n k\u1ec7. M\u00e0u t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a g\u1ed7 \u00f3c ch\u00f3 gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111\u1eb9p n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt khi k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi k\u1ec7 ti vi v\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0ng d\u1ecbu d\u00e0ng, \u1ea5m \u00e1p.<\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu gia ch\u1ee7 m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c c\u00f3 th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ch\u0103m ch\u00fat cho ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch th\u00ec c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed3 trang tr\u00ed b\u1eb1ng g\u1ed7, tre, gi\u1ea5y, c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i c\u00e2y hoa c\u1ea3nh, v\u1eadt d\u1ee5ng c\u00f3 hoa v\u0103n c\u00e2y l\u00e1 hay \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t u\u1ed1n l\u01b0\u1ee3n. Nh\u01b0ng, c\u1ea7n tr\u00e1nh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed3 trang tr\u00ed l\u00e0m b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u kim lo\u1ea1i, kim kh\u00ed.<\/p>\n<h2>N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7<\/h2>\n<p>Gia ch\u1ee7 m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00eam \u00eam gi\u1ea5c n\u1ed3ng, h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u201cl\u00ean h\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d khi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 sau:<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch, ph\u00f2ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i, \u0111\u1ee7 20m2 tr\u1edf l\u00ean, c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0110\u00f4ng, Nam ho\u1eb7c \u0110\u00f4ng Nam.<\/p>\n<p>V\u1ec1 m\u00e0u s\u1eafc, ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn gam m\u00e0u xanh l\u00e1, xanh r\u00eau \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft. Tr\u00ean n\u1ec1n xanh \u0111\u00f3, gia ch\u1ee7 t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00f4ng gian t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi, m\u00e1t m\u1ebb v\u00e0 tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y n\u0103ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. M\u1eabu ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb9p n\u00e0y gi\u00e0nh cho b\u1ea1n tr\u1ebb n\u00e0o thu\u1ed9c m\u1ec7nh M\u1ed9c v\u1edbi ti\u00eau ch\u00ed: \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u00e0 tinh t\u1ebf, chu\u1ea9n m\u00e0u m\u00e0 h\u1ee3p phong th\u1ee7y.<\/p>\n<div class=\"blog-share text-center\">\n<div class=\"social-icons share-icons share-row relative\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Trong 5 b\u1ea3n m\u1ec7nh thu\u1ed9c thuy\u1ebft Ng\u0169 h\u00e0nh, M\u1ed9c l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0ng cho s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng t\u1eeb r\u1ec5, th\u00e2n, nh\u00e1nh v\u00e0 l\u00e1. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao, c\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng ty N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0110\u1ee9c D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng t\u00f4n vinh s\u1eafc xanh cho n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t cho ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 &#82